Katrina Kaif is a British-Indian actress and model.She primarily works in the Hindi film industry, commonly referred to as Bollywood. Katrina Kaif made her acting debut in 2003 with the film "Boom," but she gained recognition and popularity with her performances in movies like "Maine Pyaar Kyun Kiya?" (2005), "Namastey London" (2007), and "New York" (2009). She has since appeared in numerous successful Bollywood films, including "Ek Tha Tiger" (2012), "Dhoom 3" (2013), "Tiger Zinda Hai" (2017), and "Bharat" (2019).
